<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!--
  Fixture: §9.1 Capability Map.
  Architect intent: customer-growth capability decomposed into four reviewable sub-capabilities,
  with business functions and a business service showing realization without application detail.
-->
